<br>
For consideration I pose this question: Would you go to a national NAACP assembly and get on the PA and say, &quot;Hey, you guys all seem really cool, but I gotta tell you, I don't give a #### about black people.&quot; Then when the beatdown ensues start screaming, &quot;Why are you guys so angry at me, I was just having fun?&quot; I think most people would call this person &quot;stupid&quot;.<br>
<br>
What they guy did was like someone heading to the schoolyard sandbox and pushing people around, then one of the people getting back up and pushing the guys face in the dirt and the guy saying, &quot;Why are you picking on me, I wuz jus havin fun *snif*&quot;. The issue wasn't with him not wanting to RP, it was 1) about bringing in yet more SH stuff and 2) about this comment:<br>
<br>
